__SqlaTable__.sql:
select "District",
          "Block",
          "Village",
          Sum(Total) as perf,
          Sum(Total) as dummy_perf,
          Count("Village") as child_count,
          Sum(Total) / Count("Village") as normalized_perf,
          TRIM(LOWER("Sex ( Male / Female )")) As Gender
   from classes
   GROUP BY "District", "Block", "Village", TRIM(LOWER("Sex ( Male / Female )"))

select "District", "Block", "Village",
          TRIM(LOWER("Sex ( Male / Female )")) As Gender,
          AVG(Total) As perf
from classes
GROUP BY "District", "Block", "Village", TRIM(LOWER("Sex ( Male / Female )"))
select "District", TRIM(LOWER("Sex ( Male / Female )")) As Gender, AVG(Total) As perf from classes GROUP BY "District", TRIM(LOWER("Sex ( Male / Female )"))

SELECT "District",
       "Block",
       "Village",
       (CAST(Total_Score AS FLOAT) / CAST(max_score AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Performance
   FROM
     (SELECT "District",
             "Block",
             "Village",
             sum(Total) as "Total_Score",
             count(*) * 20 as "max_score"
      FROM classes
      GROUP BY "District",
               "Block",
               "Village") AS A
